  textFadeDuration: 0.4
  taunts:
  - "\u201CClimbed so high\u2026 just to slide back like it\u2019s your destiny."
  - Every ladder is hope. Every snake is reality
  - "You don\u2019t lose\u2026 you return to where you belong"
  - "The board isn\u2019t unfair. You just keep choosing wrong"
  timeBetweenTaunts: 3.5
